# .lycheeignore — URL patterns the link-check workflow should skip.
# One regex per line. See https://lychee.cli.rs/ for syntax.

# OpenAI and Anthropic both return 403 to bot user agents (Cloudflare).
# These are citations in ADRs, not runtime dependencies.
https://openai\.com/index/.*
https://claude\.ai/.*

# Vendor llms.txt endpoints in known-sources.yaml are speculative until
# verified upstream — exclude from CI so an unreachable URL doesn't block merges.
# Remove specific entries here once they're verified.
https://docs\.anthropic\.com/llms\.txt
https://platform\.openai\.com/llms\.txt
https://docs\.stripe\.com/llms\.txt
https://nextjs\.org/llms\.txt
https://vercel\.com/llms\.txt
https://docs\.astro\.build/llms\.txt
https://svelte\.dev/llms\.txt
https://fastapi\.tiangolo\.com/llms\.txt
https://docs\.djangoproject\.com/llms\.txt
